sources.title: The Dog Snatcher (1931)
sources.description: Scrappy tries to rescue his dog, Yippy from a mean dog catcher. Watch on RetroFlix:Â  https://retroflix.org/the-dog-snatcher-1931/

metadata.Plot: A zealous dog catcher nabs Yippee for not having a license, though somehow he can show he belongs to several fraternal lodges, and is taken to a dog prison, complete with trigger-happy guards. Scrappy conspires to break him out, by sneaking in wearing the hide of a mutt he just skinned.
